data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value: SugarFree is a diabetes insulin management tool. It features many different tools to calculate the amount of insulin needed in different situations. It also features a daily insulin needed tool to calculate your daily insulin total based off of your weight. Everyone's body is different and many different factors go into calculating the amount of insulin needed including excersize, stress, and other factors. This should be used only as a reference, to give you a general number to start with. This software is dedicated to my husband, Lucas Smith, who is a Type 1 diabetic warrior <3
